name: GetOrder
description:
Get an Order by ID.

This service is readonly, it will not update the order just by calling it like the `GetShoppingCart` service does.

To include the result of `GetRequiredDataForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.RequiredFor` can be set to the desired level of requirements.
To include the result of `GetProductRequirementValuesForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeProductRequirements` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `GetGiftWrappingOptionsForOrder` and `GetAvailableGiftWrappingLinesForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeGiftWrapping` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `PrefigureDiscounts` and `GetPotentialDiscountsForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludePrefigureDiscounts` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `GetPickProductDiscountOptionsForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludePickProductOptions` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `ListAvailableShippingMethods`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeAvailableShippingMethods` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `GetAvailablePaymentMethods`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeAvailablePaymentMethods` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `GetAvailableRefundPaymentMethodsForOrder`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeAvailableRefundPaymentMethods` can be set to `true`.
To include the result of `ValidateOrderShipment`, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludeValidateShipment` can be set to `true`.
To include the available actions for the PaymentTransactions, the property `AdditionalOrderDataOptions.IncludePaymentTransactionActions` can be set to `true`.
auth_description: This service does not require authentication.

headers.name: EVA-User-Agent
headers.description: The user agent that is making these calls. Don't make this specific per device/browser but per application. This should be of the form: `MyFirstUserAgent/1.0.0`

headers.name: EVA-Requested-OrganizationUnitID
headers.description: The ID of the organization unit to run this request in.

headers.name: EVA-Requested-OrganizationUnit-Query
headers.description: The query that selects the organization unit to run this request in.

headers.name: EVA-IDs-Mode
headers.description: The IDs mode to run this request in. Currently only `ExternalIDs` is supported.

headers.name: EVA-IDs-BackendSystemID
headers.description: The ID of the backend system that is used to resolve the IDs.

request_samples.name: JSON
request_samples.sample:
{
  "AdditionalOrderDataOptions": {
    "IncludeAvailablePaymentMethods": true,
    "IncludeAvailableRefundPaymentMethods": true,
    "IncludeAvailableShippingMethods": true,
    "IncludeCheckoutOptions": true,
    "IncludeCustomerCustomFields": true,
    "IncludeGiftCardBusinessRules": true,
    "IncludeGiftWrapping": true,
    "IncludeOrganizationUnitData": true,
    "IncludePaymentTransactionActions": true,
    "IncludePickProductOptions": true,
    "IncludePrefigureDiscounts": true,
    "IncludeProductRequirements": true,
    "IncludeValidateShipment": true,
    "ProductProperties": [
      "string"
    ],
    "RequiredFor": 8
  },
  "IncludeAllPayments": true,
  "OrderID": 123,
  "ShowOnlyShippableLines": true
}

request_samples.name: CURL
request_samples.sample:
curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "EVA-User-Agent: MyFirstUserAgent/1.0.0" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
  --data '{
  "AdditionalOrderDataOptions": {
    "IncludeAvailablePaymentMethods": true,
    "IncludeAvailableRefundPaymentMethods": true,
    "IncludeAvailableShippingMethods": true,
    "IncludeCheckoutOptions": true,
    "IncludeCustomerCustomFields": true,
    "IncludeGiftCardBusinessRules": true,
    "IncludeGiftWrapping": true,
    "IncludeOrganizationUnitData": true,
    "IncludePaymentTransactionActions": true,
    "IncludePickProductOptions": true,
    "IncludePrefigureDiscounts": true,
    "IncludeProductRequirements": true,
    "IncludeValidateShipment": true,
    "ProductProperties": [
      "string"
    ],
    "RequiredFor": 8
  },
  "IncludeAllPayments": true,
  "OrderID": 123,
  "ShowOnlyShippableLines": true
}' \
  https://euw.acme.test.eva-online.cloud/message/GetOrder

DJ.name: Properties
DJ.description:
Flags enum, combine any of the below values:

* `0` - None
* `1` - IsPickup
* `2` - CreatedByEmployee
* `4` - IsInterbranch
* `8` - IsB2B
* `16` - Duplicated
* `32` - Autocompleted
* `128` - ReturnToSupplier
* `256` - CustomTaxesApplied
* `512` - Replenishment
* `1024` - SoldByOverridden
* `2048` - ImportedFromLiveGuard
* `4096` - IsTransferOrder
* `8192` - IsReturnsTransferOrder
* `16384` - IsOffer
* `32768` - IsUnified
* `65536` - IsReturned
* `131072` - HasReturnLines
* `262144` - DownPayment
* `524288` - Restitution
* `1048576` - Repairs
